---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
	<div class="container">
		<h1>How It Works</h1>
		
		<div class="steps-grid">
			<div class="step">
				<div class="step-icon">1</div>
				<h2>Connect Your Tools</h2>
				<p>Integrate Narthbugz with your development workflow in minutes. We support all major IDEs and version control systems.</p>
				<ul>
					<li>VS Code, IntelliJ, and other IDE plugins</li>
					<li>Git integration</li>
					<li>JIRA and other project management tools</li>
					<li>Simple API for custom integrations</li>
				</ul>
			</div>

			<div class="step">
				<div class="step-icon">2</div>
				<h2>Automatic Time Tracking</h2>
				<p>Our tools silently track time as your team works, requiring zero manual input from developers.</p>
				<ul>
					<li>IDE activity monitoring</li>
					<li>Git commit association</li>
					<li>Smart idle detection</li>
					<li>Task context awareness</li>
				</ul>
			</div>

			<div class="step">
				<div class="step-icon">3</div>
				<h2>Data Analysis</h2>
				<p>We analyze your team's historical data to build accurate time-series models of productivity.</p>
				<ul>
					<li>Task completion patterns</li>
					<li>Team velocity metrics</li>
					<li>Seasonal variations</li>
					<li>Developer specializations</li>
				</ul>
			</div>

			<div class="step">
				<div class="step-icon">4</div>
				<h2>Monte Carlo Simulation</h2>
				<p>Using your team's actual data, we simulate thousands of possible futures to generate accurate predictions.</p>
				<ul>
					<li>Confidence intervals</li>
					<li>Risk assessment</li>
					<li>Timeline forecasting</li>
					<li>Resource allocation</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</Layout>

<style>
	.container {
		max-width: 1200px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 4rem 2rem;
	}

	h1 {
		font-size: 3rem;
		font-weight: 800;
		margin: 0 0 3rem;
		text-align: center;
		background: linear-gradient(83.21deg, #3245ff 0%, #bc52ee 100%);
		-webkit-background-clip: text;
		-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
		line-height: 1.1;
		letter-spacing: -0.02em;
	}

	.steps-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
		gap: 2rem;
		margin-top: 2rem;
	}

	.step {
		background: var(--bg-primary);
		padding: 2rem;
		border-radius: 1rem;
		backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
		transition: all 0.3s ease;
		box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 2px 4px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
	}

	.step:hover {
		transform: translateY(-5px);
		box-shadow: 0 10px 15px -3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 4px 6px -2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
	}

	.step-icon {
		width: 3rem;
		height: 3rem;
		background: linear-gradient(83.21deg, #3245ff 0%, #bc52ee 100%);
		color: white;
		border-radius: 50%;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		font-weight: bold;
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}

	h2 {
		margin: 0 0 1rem;
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		color: var(--text-primary);
		font-weight: 700;
		letter-spacing: -0.01em;
	}

	p {
		margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
		color: var(--text-secondary);
		line-height: 1.6;
		font-size: 1.125rem;
	}

	ul {
		margin: 0;
		padding-left: 1.5rem;
		color: #4b5563;
		line-height: 1.6;
	}

	li {
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.container {
			padding: 2rem 1rem;
		}

		h1 {
			font-size: 2.5rem;
		}

		.steps-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}
	}
</style>
